These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: woodworking, camping, chess, cabbaged-games
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, disaster, drama, superhero
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: folk, funk, reggae, rock
City: miami, marseilles, liverpool, san-francisco
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, raspberry, lemon, strawberry
 1. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching disaster movies##1
 2. the fan of rock is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the person eating strawberry##2
 3. the person traveling to miami is the person eating strawberry##1
 4. the person traveling to marseilles is on the left of the person traveling to liverpool##1
 5. the person eating cabbage is between the person who's hobby is woodworking and the fan of reggae##2
 6. the person traveling to san-francisco is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 7. the person eating raspberry is the person who's hobby is chess##1
 8. the person who's hobby is cabbaged-games is on the left of the person watching superhero movies##1
 9. the person watching drama movies is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
10. the fan of folk is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |         3          |     4     |
| Hobby           | chess | woodworking   | cabbaged-games | camping |
| Movie-Genre   | crime      | disaster | drama              | superhero |
| Music-Genre   | folk       | funk     | rock               | reggae    |
| City           | marseilles        | liverpool     | san-francisco           | miami       |
| Food     | raspberry | lemon     | cabbage                | strawberry      |

