.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-2::.
There 4 different types of food: blueberry, lemon, pineapple, tomato
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, freelancer, police-officer, project-manager
There are 4 different favourite colors: fuchsia, yellow, turquise, green
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, rock-climbing, sudoku, skydiving
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: december, january, february, september
 1. the police-officer is on the right of the person eating lemon##1
 2. the person who likes fuchsia is on the right of the person eating blueberry##1
 3. the freelancer is between the person eating pineapple and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
 4. the person who likes green is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person who's hobby is sudoku is the freelancer##1
 6. the police-officer is on the left of the electrician##1
 7. the project-manager is on the left of the person who likes yellow##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in january is on the left of the police-officer##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in february is on the left of the electrician##1
10. the police-officer is on the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
11. the person who's birthday is in december is the person eating pineapple##1
12. the person eating blueberry is the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |     2      |       3        |      4      |
| Food          | pineapple       | lemon      | blueberry      | tomato      |
| Job           | project-manager | freelancer | police-officer | electrician |
| Color   | green          | yellow       | turquise            | fuchsia      |
| Hobby           | board-games            | sudoku    | rock-climbing           | skydiving       |
| Birthday         | december        | january    | february         | september  |

