There are 4 different nationalities: british, colombian, japanese, pakistani
House: palace, wooden, farmhouse, colonial
The people have 4 different jobs:  musician, software-developer, accountant, nurse
 1. the british is on the right of the person driving the train##1
 2. the palace house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 3. the palace house is on the left of the japanese##1
 4. the palace house is the software-developer##1
 5. the wooden house is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
 6. the person eating asparagus is between the person driving the van and the musician##2
 7. the british is on the left of the person eating strawberry##1
 8. the person eating grapefruit is the accountant##1
 9. the british is the colonial house##1
10. the colombian is on the far left##1
11. the colombian is the musician##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | banana    | asparagus  | strawberry | grapefruit |
| Transport   | train   | motorbike        | van | tram     |
| Nationality   | colombian | british    | pakistani  | japanese   |
| House           | farmhouse     | colonial      | palace | wooden        |
| Job         | musician      | nurse | software-developer      | accountant     |

