.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, reading, fishing, card-games
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: january, august, september, december
There are 4 different favourite colors: red, fuchsia, black, green
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, parkour, snowboarding, soccer
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, quad-bike, roller, van
 1. the person driving the roller is the person who's birthday is in january##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is between the person who likes red and the person who likes fuchsia##2
 3. the person who likes red is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
 4. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person who's sport is cricket##1
 5. the person who likes fuchsia is between the person who's sport is cricket and the person driving the bus##2
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the far left##1
 7. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the person who likes black##1
 8. the person who's hobby is gardening is the person driving the van##1
 9. the person who's hobby is reading is between the person driving the quad-bike and the person who likes black##2
10. the person who's birthday is in december is on the far left##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |      3      |      4       |
| Hobby      | card-games     | reading | fishing    | gardening          |
| Birthday          | december | january     | september | august         |
| Color   | black    | fuchsia       | green         | red        |
| Sport         | soccer  | parkour     | cricket     | snowboarding |
| Transport     | bus     | roller      | quad-bike   | van          |

