The people prefer 4 different music-genres: funk, classical, metal, trance
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, crime, martial-arts, thriller
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, german, mexican, spanish
 1. the person watching thriller movies is the old-henry-smoker##1
 2. the person watching thriller movies is on the left of the german##1
 3. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who likes green##1
 4. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the person watching crime movies##1
 5. the prince-smoker is on the far right##1
 6. the spanish is on the right of the person who likes amber##1
 7. the person watching crime movies is on the right of the fan of trance##1
 8. the person who likes green is on the right of the person watching action movies##1
 9. the dannemann-smoker is on the left of the fan of classical##1
10. the old-henry-smoker is between the dannemann-smoker and the fan of funk##2
11. the canadian is on the right of the davidoff-smoker##1
12. the person who likes chestnut is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |      3       |      4       |
