There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, mirinda, iced-tea, hot-chocolate
There are 4 different nationalities: american, dutch, french, turkish
City: hamburg, rome, liverpool, new-york
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the french is on the left of the person traveling to rome##1
 3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1
 4. the person eating lemon is on the right of the person traveling to new-york##1
 5. the person eating pomegranate is on the right of the person who's birthday is in february##1
 6. the turkish is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 7. the american is the person drinking mirinda##1
 8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person eating avocado##2
 9. the person who's birthday is in september is on the far left##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is between the person eating avocado and the person who's birthday is in july##2
11. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |      2      |      3      |     4     |
| Food          | avocado       | lemon       | pomegranate | banana    |
| Birthday         | september     | february | july | january     |
