 5. the person who's birthday is in april is the social-worker##1
 6. the fan of indie is the person playing poker##1
 7. the person who growsorchid is the person playing canasta##1
 8. the person playing poker is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
 9. the fan of indie is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
10. the fan of salsa is on the left of the person who's birthday is in bellflowering##1
11. the person who's birthday is in bellflowering is between the social-worker and the person who growsorchid##2
12. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who growsazalea and the person playing poker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |       2        |    3     |     4      |
| Game      | domino      | poker         | canasta | whist      |
| Job           | social-worker | police-officer | designer | doctor     |
| Music-Genre   | salsa         | indie          | ambient  | electronic |
| Birthday         | april        | bellflowering  | september | march   |
| Flower     | bellflower    | poppy         | orchid     | azalea     |

