.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-18::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: november, july, june, august
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, water, juice, tea
4 different pets are kept: frog, goat, goldfish, snake
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: lacrosse, soccer, swimming, tennis
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: orchid, iris, daffodil, marigold
 1. the owner of the snake is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who growsiris##2
 2. the owner of the snake is on the right of the person drinking tea##1
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is the person who growsdaffodil##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the far right##1
 5. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in november is the person drinking tea##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person drinking juice##1
10. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is between the person drinking tea and the person who's sport is lacrosse##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3     |   4    |
| Birthday          | november  | august  | july  | june   |
| Beverage   | tea     | 7up | juice     | water |
| Pet           | goldfish   | snake     | goat      | frog   |
| Sport         | swimming   | tennis    | lacrosse  | soccer |
| Flower     | orchid | marigold     | iris | daffodil |

