.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-19::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: fanta, juice, milk, sprite
There 4 different types of food: cherry, apricot, nectarine, grapefruit
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, february, may, march
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, swisher, blend, ritmeester
The people use 4 different means of transport: airplane, jet-ski, scooter, van
 1. the person who's birthday is in may is the person eating apricot##1
 2. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
 3. the person drinking juice is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person who's birthday is in march##2
 4. the person who's birthday is in march is the old-henry-smoker##1
 5. the person drinking fanta is between the person drinking juice and the person driving the van##2
 6. the person driving the jet-ski is on the right of the person eating grapefruit##1
 7. the blend-smoker is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating cherry is the person driving the scooter##1
 9. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
10. the person drinking milk is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |       4       |
| Beverage      | sprite    | juice     | fanta        | milk          |
| Food         | grapefruit | apricot   | cherry        | nectarine |
| Birthday           | june   | may | march | february      |
| Cigar   | ritmeester    | swisher      | old-henry          | blend        |
| Transport     | airplane  | jet-ski   | scooter      | van           |

