.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-2-20::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: magic-tricks, skydiving, traveling, woodworking
There are 4 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade, milk, juice
There 4 different types of food: garlic, papaya, kiwi, plum
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, handball, parkour, sailing
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, comedy, sports, spy
 1. the person drinking juice is the person eating papaya##1
 2. the person watching spy movies is between the person eating plum and the person who's sport is badminton##2
 3. the person watching comedy movies is between the person who's sport is handball and the person watching sports movies##2
 4. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 5. the person drinking milk is on the right of the person who's sport is handball##1
 6. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
 8. the person drinking milk is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 9. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
10. the person who's hobby is magic-tricks is the person eating garlic##1
11. the person eating garlic is the person who's sport is sailing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |      3      |      4       |
| Hobby         | traveling  | skydiving | woodworking | magic-tricks |
| Beverage   | juice      | lemonade   | milk      | almond-milk    |
| Food   | papaya  | kiwi | plum        | garlic     |
| Sport         | badminton  | handball  | parkour     | sailing      |
| Movie-Genre     | scientific | spy      | comedy   | sports       |

 